<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome to College Migration</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome <%= name %>!</h1>
    
    <p>Your account has been created by our admin team. Here are your login details:</p>
    
    <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <%= tempPassword %></p>
        <p>Please login and change your password immediately:</p>
        <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" 
           style="background: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; 
                  text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
            Login Now
        </a>
    </div>

    <p>If you need any assistance, contact our support team at 
       <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a></p>

    <footer style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px;">
        <p>Best regards,<br>College Migration Team</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html> 